::DevilDuer::

DevilDuer growls at Lady Hawk, walking closer to her. He didn't like this 
bot, and he was showing it.

"Alliright, fine," he says, "I'm DevilDuer, as you already know that is 
Hurricane, and we're part of the Alliance."

He moves his gun dangeroustly, ready to shoot her. "Now why in the pit are 
you here?"
